<p>We are getting more and more questions about iCloud, and if you go through the <a href="https://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/tagged/icloud" class="post-tag" title="show questions tagged &#39;icloud&#39;" rel="tag">icloud</a> you will find a lot of them relate to people misunderstanding iCloud and how it works, including backup.</p>

